PN,36201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773245482
OL,3,CGirl who suffers 13-hour seizures: 'I
OL,4,Ccan't go out. I don't have friends'
OL,6,FA teenage girl who struggles to
OL,7,Fsocialise due to a rare form of
OL,8,Fepilepsy which can cause 13-hour
OL,9,Fseizures says pioneering treatment
OL,10,Fcould allow her to "make friends".
OL,12,FGrace Pagdin's condition is so severe
OL,13,Fshe has been left unable to leave the
OL,14,Fhouse and has only been to school five
OL,15,Ftimes in the last 18 months.
OL,17,FThe 15-year-old, from Sheffield, has
OL,18,Fbeen recommended for treatment called
OL,19,Fdeep brain stimulation (DBS), which
OL,20,Finvolves implanting electrodes in the
OL,21,Fbrain.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773245482
OL,3,CGirl who suffers 13-hour seizures: 'I
OL,4,Ccan't go out. I don't have friends'
OL,6,FBut her family are having to fundraise
OL,7,Fto cover the #40,000 cost, as it is
OL,8,Funavailable on the NHS.
OL,10,FGrace said: "I can't go out with
OL,11,Fmates, I don't have any friends. If it
OL,12,Fcould give me a normal life, maybe I
OL,13,Fcould make friends and go out with
OL,14,Fthem."
OL,16,FGrace was taken to Sheffield
OL,17,FChildren's Hospital after she had a
OL,18,Fseizure as an eight-year-old.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773245482
OL,3,CGirl who suffers 13-hour seizures: 'I
OL,4,Ccan't go out. I don't have friends'
OL,6,FDoctors initially told her family it
OL,7,Fwas a "common seizure", but problems
OL,8,Fcontinued and she was later diagnosed
OL,9,Fwith a form of epilepsy called
OL,10,Fmyoclonic status epilepticus.
OL,12,FHer mother, Emma, said: "When she goes
OL,13,Fin to seizure, she could be in it for
OL,14,Ftwo hours. We give her medication, she
OL,15,Fcan come round for an hour and a half,
OL,16,Fhave something to eat and the next
OL,17,Fthing she's slumped over having more
OL,18,Fseizures.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773245482
OL,3,CGirl who suffers 13-hour seizures: 'I
OL,4,Ccan't go out. I don't have friends'
OL,6,F"Grace is just crying to me all the
OL,7,Ftime, asking me 'why has this happened
OL,8,Fto me? Why does nobody like me? Why
OL,9,Fcan't I go to a sleepover? Why can't I
OL,10,Fgo for a walk on my own?'
OL,12,F"It's heartbreaking, I can't sleep
OL,13,Fbecause I'm so upset that life hasn't
OL,14,Fturned out for Grace like it has for
OL,15,Fher sister and her brother who've had
OL,16,Fnormal teenage lives."
OL,18,FMedication has failed to address the
OL,19,Fproblem.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773245482
OL,3,CGirl who suffers 13-hour seizures: 'I
OL,4,Ccan't go out. I don't have friends'
OL,6,F"It's really quite rare for a child
OL,7,Fnot to respond to medications the way
OL,8,FGrace doesn't respond and the amount
OL,9,Fof seizures she has," Emma said.
OL,11,FThe family have set up an online
OL,12,Ffundraiser to pay for DBS, in which
OL,13,Felectrodes are implanted in the brain
OL,14,Fand connected to a pacemaker-like
OL,15,Fdevice in the chest, which sends
OL,16,Felectrical pulses to regulate abnormal
OL,17,Fbrain signals and improve motor
OL,18,Fsymptoms.
OL,20,FMore than #11,000 has been raised so
OL,21,Ffar.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
